# CODEOWNERS
# This file defines code ownership for automatic PR review assignments
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
*                           @data-team @tech-lead

# Documentation
*.md                        @data-team @docs-team
/docs/                      @docs-team @product-team
/README.md                  @tech-lead @product-owner

# Core library code
/src/data_quality_toolkit/  @data-team @tech-lead
/src/data_quality_toolkit/profiling/   @data-team @analytics-team
/src/data_quality_toolkit/assessment/  @data-team @quality-team
/src/data_quality_toolkit/exporters/   @data-team @bi-team
/src/data_quality_toolkit/semantics/   @analytics-team @bi-team
/src/data_quality_toolkit/transformer/ @data-team
/src/data_quality_toolkit/workflow/    @data-team @devops-team

# Power BI specific components
/src/data_quality_toolkit/exporters/bi/        @bi-team
/src/data_quality_toolkit/exporters/bi/powerbi/ @bi-team @bi-lead
/docs/powerbi/              @bi-team @docs-team
/scripts/*powerbi*.py       @bi-team

# API and UI
/api/                       @backend-team @tech-lead
/ui/                        @frontend-team @ux-team
/cli/                       @backend-team @devops-team

# Security-sensitive files
/src/data_quality_toolkit/exporters/bi/powerbi/rls/  @bi-team @security-team
/SECURITY.md                @security-team @tech-lead
*.tmsl.json                 @bi-team @security-team
